<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.10">
<l>aṅkama lakkaṇṇaṉ taṉṉai yacōtaikku</l>
<l>maṅkainal lārkaḷtām vantu muṟaippaṭṭa</l>
<l>aṅkavar collaip putuvaikkōṉ paṭṭaṉcol</l>
<l>iṅkivai vallavark kētamoṉ ṟillaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master these words here by the scholar king of Putuvai</l>
<l rend="indent">about the regularly occurring complaints of those there,</l>
<l rend="indent">the good girls coming to Yaśodā,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the beautiful lotus eyed boy,</l>
<l>there will be no suffering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
